# LearnHub: Your Center for Skill Enhancement

## 📘 Project Overview

LearnHub is a full-stack online learning platform (OLP) designed to help students, teachers, and admins interact over a centralized education system. It allows users to register, browse, enroll, and manage online courses. The platform supports role-based dashboards, user authentication, payment features, and certification.

---

## 🎯 Key Features

* **User Roles**: Student, Teacher, Admin
* **Authentication**: Register/Login for all users
* **Course Management**:

  * Teachers: Add/edit/manage courses
  * Students: Browse/enroll/track progress
* **Dashboard Views**:

  * Separate dashboards for students, teachers, and admins
* **Certification**: Certificate issued upon course completion
* **Payment System**: For premium courses

---

## 🧑‍💻 Technologies Used

| Layer      | Tech Stack                                    |
| ---------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Frontend   | React.js (Vite), Axios, Bootstrap/Material UI |
| Backend    | Node.js, Express.js                           |
| Database   | MongoDB (with Mongoose ODM)                   |
| Auth       | Placeholder middleware (JWT suggested)        |
| Deployment | Vercel (frontend), Render (backend)           |

