## 🧪 Case Study: Learning a New Skill

* Sarah (Student) registers on LearnHub
* She finds and enrolls in "Web Development Fundamentals"
* She completes video lessons and assignments
* Uses dashboard to track progress
* Takes the final quiz and gets certified

John (Teacher):

* Adds courses, uploads materials, and checks enrollments

Admin:

* Manages users, monitors system, and updates courses

